/***********************************************************************
 *		MSG_SAF_GAME_CARD_END_OF_QUIZ
 ***********************************************************************
 * SYNOPSIS:	    all questions asked
 * PASS:            none
 * RETURN:          none
 *
 * REVISION HISTORY:
 *	Name	Date		Description
 *	----	----		-----------
 *	gene	4/13/99		Initial Revision
